      "raw_text": "Telephone girls In Idaho are max\ning an effort to secure higher wages\nand public sympathy is with them\nto such extent tina. at Pocateilo 200\nphones have been ordered taken out\nand the trades council is behind the\nfight. The company refuses to meet\nthe operators or arbitrate. An in\ncrease of $40 per month is asked\nover a minimum wage of $40 per\nmonth.\n\n\nBusiness men generally support\nthe girls contention that they can\nnot live decently on the present\nrate of pay.\n\n\nAt Wallace the girls are also on a\nstrike and the company Is having\nmore or less trouble over the wage\nquestion in other parts of the state."
    }
